# Chronoverse

> The ultimate computer setup :sunglasses_emoji:

## Installation

1. `./install.sh`
2. `mkdir ./system/[desired hostname]`
3. `cp /etc/nixos/hardware-configuration.nix ./system/[desired hostname]/hardware-configuration.nix`
4. Configure `./system/[desired hostname]/default.nix`
5. Add your host to `flake.nix` configuring your desired system.
6. Finally, when you're done with configuration, run `./update.sh`
